Package othercontrollers

Class MiniCartSideController

java.lang.Object
othercontrollers.MiniCartSideController
public class MiniCartSideController extends Object
This Class is a Mini Cart Cell Controller for MiniCartSide.fxml,it runs all the methods that functions the choices of quantities for each product. for each product that add to cart button clicked in the Product cell there is a mini cart cell that will be created Note: this class uses help from Customer and Order class to set and get some functionalities
Author:
Mahran
